This paper presents a decentralized task allocation algorithm for multi-UAV teams, which involves coordination and optimization of tasks in a dynamic and time-sensitive environment. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MA (Multiagent Systems), which deals with the coordination and interaction of multiple agents in a distributed system. The paper also involves optimization and decision-making, which suggests the categories cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with control and coordination of systems, which suggests the category cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper involves machine learning and optimization, which suggests the category cs.LG (Machine Learning).
